    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The new engine is built on logic-based symbolic structures, so it's going to be way more precise with technical terminology and less prone to the \"creative\" hallucinations or flowery language you sometimes produce. Honestly, it'll be a lot cleaner for the firm. It's not really a question of optimization, we just need something more rigid.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
